    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/2cc7455f960f988a7f43dcfb82342429.poster.avif?t=1748567558\" width=640 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/2cc7455f960f988a7f43dcfb82342429.webm?t=1748567558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/2cc7455f960f988a7f43dcfb82342429.mp4?t=1748567558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RESIDUAL SOUL is a singleplayer narrative short-story heavily inspired by the creepypasta horror genre.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/ee3f86212293f51b996ae3d0a92a678c.poster.avif?t=1748567558\" width=640 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/ee3f86212293f51b996ae3d0a92a678c.webm?t=1748567558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/ee3f86212293f51b996ae3d0a92a678c.mp4?t=1748567558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After being taken to a purgatory-like forest with the promise of speaking to his deceased wife, Matt must survive his time there and bring peace to the souls who still linger. Manage threats like violent souls and fluctuating power levels while unveiling the stories of those who came before you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/d6099446651a661509d44ff86293a3a3.poster.avif?t=1748567558\" width=640 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/d6099446651a661509d44ff86293a3a3.webm?t=1748567558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/d6099446651a661509d44ff86293a3a3.mp4?t=1748567558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Melancholic atmosphere and stunning visuals</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Thoughtful sound design</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Skilled voice acting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Dynamic storyline<br><br><strong>CONTENT WARNING:</strong><br><i>RESIDUAL SOUL FEATURES MATURE THEMES DEALING WITH LOSS OF LOVED ONES AND SUICIDE. IF SUCH TOPICS MAY EFFECT YOU NEGATIVELY, KINDLY PASS ON THIS GAME.</i></p>",
